I just wanted to take a moment to thank you all for being such an important part of my life this year. Meeting you in the space may have been unexpected, but I am so grateful for the friendship that has developed as a result. You have brought so much fun and support into my life, and I am grateful to have you as part of my community from close or from far. 
Some of you definitely change my life in a way or another. 
Thank you for being there for me through all of life's ups and downs. Here's to many more years of friendship and laughter!

Le Sheraf.
